Output demo.gif

Require vhs

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

# ── Install ───────────────────────────────────────────────

Type "npx tenkai-mcp install"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3500ms

# Select option 1 (Claude Code user-level)
Type "1"
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

# ── Search ───────────────────────────────────────────────

Sleep 800ms
Type "node demo-search.mjs 'open source LLM inference'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 4000ms

Sleep 3s
